BRANCH-0.8
============================================================================

RELEASE-0.8.5 (January 24, 2007) 
RELEASE-0.8.4 (January 16, 2007) 
RELEASE-0.8.3 (January 10, 2007) 
RELEASE-0.8.2 (January 8, 2007)
RELEASE-0.8.1 (December 21, 2006) 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Added the externals and utils package which are used as a substitute for
	the wx-toolsbox and wx-utils packages which are distributed with Confix.

*) Refactoring: Namespaces
	+ Removed ccm::local namespace from local Components interfaces.
	+ Added ccmtools::corba to IDL Components interfaces.
	+ Changed ccm:remote namespace to ccmtools::remote namespace.
	+ Changed the namespace order from e.g. world::ccmtools::remote 
	  to ccmtools::remote::world.

*) Refactoring: CCM.h
	+ Moved all implementations in separate *.cc files.
	+ Added "typedef SmartPtr<class> SmartPtr" to each C++ class. 
	+ Changed the name from CCM.h to ccmtools.h
	+ Changed the name from CCM.idl to ccmtools.idl
	
*) Refactoring: HomeFinder
	Implemented HomeFinder singleton within the Components namespace.
	

BRANCH-0.7
============================================================================

RELEASE-0.7.6 (, 2006)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Bugfix: LocalComponents/CCM.h 
	Added virtual destructors and virtual inheritance declarations.

*) Bugfix: Interix (reported by Duft Markus)
	Added _CCM_EXPORT_DECL_ Makro to HomeFinder.h and CCMContainer.h which
	uses static attributes.


RELEASE-0.7.3 (October 16, 2006)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Refactoring: Upgrade to Confix2
	Added Confix2.pkg and Confix2.dir files to build the C++ runtime unsing
	Confix2.
	

RELEASE-0.7.2 (October 5, 2006)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Refactoring: Upgrade to wx-utils-3.1.0
	Changed namespace WX::Utils to wx::utils
	
*) Refactoring: Changed namespace ccm::local::Components to Components::ccm::local

*) Bugfix: merged changes from RELEASE-0_6_14
	=> ccm/local/HomeFinder.cc
	=> utils/measurement/Timer.cc
	

RELEASE-0.7.1 (September 7, 2006)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
*) Bugfix: ccm/remote/Makefile.py
 	Added optional package-name and package-version definitions.


RELEASE-0.7.0 (August 17, 2006)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
o) Refactoring: 
	Changed directory names from CCM_Local, CCM_Remote to local, remote.
	Removed OCL and Python code.

o) Bugfixes: We have merged all bugfixes made in RELEASE-0_6_6-BRANCH to the trunk.
